Avaliable commands:

  build:            runs clean, restore, test, version, publish and package
  clean:            removes the /bin/ dir contents
  dotnet-restore:   runs dotnet restore command
  dotnet-test:      runs the dotnet test command
  test:             another command to run the tests
  publish-app:      runs dotnet publish command in release configuration
  version:          adds current version to version.txt
  package-app:      packages the application into a .zip file
  build-and-test:   runs restore, build and test
  run:              runs the appliation
